<h2>About Mark</h2>
<a class="fancybox" title="Mark Edge" href="https://cointelegraph.com/storage/uploads/view/e22335d3415e4682b389384d0148a42b.jpg" rel="gallery"><img title="Mark Edge" src="https://cointelegraph.com/storage/uploads/view/e22335d3415e4682b389384d0148a42b.jpg" alt="Mark Edge" /></a>
